"531","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;><font face=EYInterstate Light lang=EN-US style=font-size:9.0pt;>In planning and performing our audit of the"
"532","financial statements of Dreyfus Intermediate Municipal Bond Fund, Inc. (the"
"533","&#8220;Company&#8221;) as of and for the year ended May 31, 2011, in accordance with the standards of the Public Company Accounting Oversight Board (United States), we"
"534","considered the Company&#8217;s internal control over financial reporting, including"
"535","controls over safeguarding securities, as a basis for designing our auditing"
"536","procedures for the purpose of expressing our opinion on the financial"
"537","statements and to comply with the requirements of Form N-SAR, but not for the"
